00:09:53.718 --> 00:09:55.553
I think I overreacted.

00:09:58.431 --> 00:09:59.432
Not at all.

00:09:59.724 --> 00:10:01.309
I jumped to conclusions.

00:10:02.519 --> 00:10:03.645
You can catch

00:10:05.230 --> 00:10:06.481
